    '2 cups flour (plain), ½ quart milk, 1 teaspoon salt, 6 eggs',
    'Combine milk and eggs and beat together. Add sifted flour and salt to egg mixture and beat in slowly. Pour into hot oiled muffin tins. Bake in oven 450 degrees Fahrenheit for approximately 45 minutes.',
